These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, drama, family, documentary
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, hip-hop, indie, house
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, russian, italian, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, snowmobile, skateboard
1. the russian is the fan of house##1
2. the italian is between the person watching family movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
3. the russian is the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the fan of jazz is on the left of the indian##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching family movies##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
8. the indian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching drama movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | documentary   | spy  | family  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | house    | jazz      | indie    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | russian | italian | indian |
| Transport     | skateboard  | scooter       | helicopter    | snowmobile     |

