.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, skydiving, puzzles, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, mystery, crime
4 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, cat, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, biathlon, sailing, handball
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person watching crime movies is between the owner of the cat and the person who's sport is tennis##2
6. the person who's sport is handball is between the person watching crime movies and the owner of the mouse##2
7. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
8. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
9. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | skydiving    | puzzles  | chess    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror      | documentary  | crime  | mystery |
| Pet           | mouse      | cat       | turtle      | ferret       |
| Sport         | biathlon    | handball | sailing | tennis |

