.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, orange, cauliflower, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, video-games, board-games, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, journalist, freelancer, entrepreneur
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, bike, airplane
1. the freelancer is the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the journalist is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person eating lime is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
9. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person eating cauliflower and the journalist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | orange | cauliflower     | lime   | apple     |
| Hobby       | video-games   | cooking   | board-games | hiking |
| Job         | musician   | freelancer | entrepreneur       | journalist    |
| Transport   | bike    | snowmobile | van  | airplane    |

