.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, engineer, project-manager, journalist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, zombie, adventure, sports
4 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig, cat, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, baseball, skiing, swimming
 1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching sports movies is the paramedic##1
 3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the person watching zombie movies is the project-manager##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the engineer is between the owner of the rat and the journalist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | paramedic  | journalist | engineer     | project-manager |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | drama  | adventure | zombie       |
| Pet           | guinea-pig       | turtle    | cat      | rat           |
| Sport         | basketball | baseball   | swimming   | skiing         |

