 7. the analyst is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 8. the manager is the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the person eating mango is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person watching disaster movies##2
10. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1

