There 4 different types of food: apricot, pepper, pineapple, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, board-games, writing, reading
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person eating apricot is the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is between the person eating apricot and the person eating pineapple##2
 9. the person eating peas is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person eating apricot and the person eating pineapple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up    | fanta      | iced-tea |
| Food       | apricot        | peas       | pineapple       | pepper     |
| Hobby      | writing | singing | reading | board-games        |
| Pet        | goldfish       | mouse     | hedgehog         | cat           |

